277
00:18:22,453 --> 00:18:27,820
-Say you're sorry. Say you're sorry.
-I'm sorry. Kind of.

278
00:18:27,891 --> 00:18:29,005
-It's not working.
-Not really.

279
00:18:29,077 --> 00:18:31,019
-French?
-Get outta here.

280
00:18:31,093 --> 00:18:33,034
-Sabrina!
-I'm coming, Mom!

281
00:18:33,877 --> 00:18:36,880
