282
00:18:36,951 --> 00:18:40,363
Yes, yes, yes, yes.
I was thinking Jude, Chapter three.

283
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:42,008
"The quality of mercy is not strained.

284
00:18:42,119 --> 00:18:44,559
