311
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:03,798
You've known me since I was just
a wee little thing, and now...

312
00:20:03,868 --> 00:20:06,454
-Pigtails and braces.
-Yes!

313
00:20:06,524 --> 00:20:09,342
-Look at you now. So wonderful.
-That's right. Can you believe it?

314
00:20:09,407 --> 00:20:12,920
I tell you what,
I'm gonna have to leave you lovebirds

315
00:20:12,993 --> 00:20:15,226
and get on back to the church

316
00:20:15,293 --> 00:20:17,683
so we can have
this marvelous wedding of yours.

317
00:20:17,756 --> 00:20:19,482
Thank you!

318
00:20:19,551 --> 00:20:21,177
-Be sweet, dear.
-Thank you so much.

319
00:20:21,247 --> 00:20:23,319
-And take care.
-Thanks.

320
00:20:23,421 --> 00:20:24,851
-We'll talk soon.
-All right, Rev.

321
00:20:24,926 --> 00:20:27,061
-All the best. See you all. Bye-bye.
-All right, see you tomorrow.

322
00:20:27,130 --> 00:20:28,345
-Take care.
-Bye.

323
00:20:30,397 --> 00:20:32,122
