340
00:22:11,971 --> 00:22:14,341
Ain't nothing wrong
with a little biscuit and gravy.

341
00:22:15,621 --> 00:22:17,215
Please.

342
00:22:17,955 --> 00:22:19,551
Don't walk away from your future.

343
00:22:19,622 --> 00:22:23,005
Let's go, let's go, let's go.
Please get me out of here.

344
00:22:27,686 --> 00:22:29,476
See, that's what I'm talking about.

345
00:22:29,574 --> 00:22:32,443
-Be careful with that.
-He know what he doing.

346
00:22:35,209 --> 00:22:39,909
Shonda, I am trying to be nice,
but who are they trying to impress?

347
00:22:39,975 --> 00:22:41,983
