354
00:22:57,033 --> 00:22:58,976
No, but, Mrs. Watson,
the calligrapher broke her arm

355
00:22:59,050 --> 00:23:01,472
and she can't finish the guest cards.
So, I was...

356
00:23:03,690 --> 00:23:07,332
