400
00:25:05,589 --> 00:25:08,653
Now, now, this is not
for your honeymoon night. No, no, no.

401
00:25:08,723 --> 00:25:11,985
No, this is for when you guys fight
or you want something expensive.

402
00:25:12,051 --> 00:25:13,041
You put this on

403
00:25:13,113 --> 00:25:15,622
-and you cook him some dinner.
-Got it.

404
00:25:15,625 --> 00:25:17,366
I might not know anything
about marriage,

405
00:25:17,446 --> 00:25:20,240
but I do know
how to help you guys stay married.

406
00:25:20,307 --> 00:25:21,803
Auntie, I think you got the perfect one.

407
00:25:21,877 --> 00:25:23,885
-I love it! It's the best.
-Good!

408
00:25:24,149 --> 00:25:25,973
-I love you, chérie.
-I love you so much.

409
00:25:27,252 --> 00:25:28,779
Do everybody out here
got their own boat?

410
00:25:28,853 --> 00:25:31,186
I don't wanna get on
no boats around here.

411
00:25:31,252 --> 00:25:33,195
Make you feel
like they're taking you back to Africa.

412
00:25:33,459 --> 00:25:34,573
This place is amazing.

413
00:25:36,215 --> 00:25:39,026
This is so beautiful.
Look at these houses!

