I would've went to Mexico for that.

424
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:06,992
What a brother will do for the taco.

425
00:26:07,066 --> 00:26:09,136
And a burrito and rice and beans.

426
00:26:09,207 --> 00:26:11,247
