448
00:27:16,350 --> 00:27:18,137
-Willie Earl.
-Hey, whassup, Jay?

449
00:27:18,527 --> 00:27:20,982
-How you doing, man? Good to see you.
-My love to you, boy.

450
00:27:21,055 --> 00:27:22,614
Long time no see.

451
00:27:23,387 --> 00:27:25,212
Welcome to the Vineyard, Mom.

452
00:27:25,277 --> 00:27:27,863
-You sent a car to get your mother?
-Only the best for you.

453
00:27:27,933 --> 00:27:30,268
Well, the best would've been
for you to pick me up.

454
00:27:30,334 --> 00:27:32,534
I love you, too, Mom.
Mom, this is Sabrina.

455
00:27:32,603 --> 00:27:33,654
Hello.

456
00:27:37,216 --> 00:27:40,509
Hi! Mrs. Taylor!
It is so nice to finally meet you!

457
00:27:40,572 --> 00:27:41,818
Isn't she great, Mom?

458
00:27:41,886 --> 00:27:44,189
I'm sorry. I just...

459
00:27:44,254 --> 00:27:46,643
I didn't think a handshake
expressed the moment, you know?

460
00:27:46,719 --> 00:27:47,799
No.

461
00:27:47,870 --> 00:27:49,977
I'm a hugger. I like to hug.

462
00:27:50,047 --> 00:27:51,123
I can see that.

463
00:27:52,287 --> 00:27:53,269
Sorry.

464
00:27:53,342 --> 00:27:54,969
I'm Claudine Watson.

465
00:27:55,999 --> 00:27:57,013
Pam Taylor.

466
00:27:57,085 --> 00:28:00,699
Well, may I say that you've certainly
raised a wonderful man.

467
00:28:00,767 --> 00:28:02,262
Thank you. He is wonderful.

468
00:28:02,338 --> 00:28:04,248
I wish I could say the same about you
and your daughter.

469
00:28:08,832 --> 00:28:12,792
I said that the wrong way.
I mean, I wish I had met her earlier,

470
00:28:12,865 --> 00:28:17,469
-before now, and then I could say...
-This is my family.

471
00:28:17,568 --> 00:28:19,542
Shonda. She is my mom's best friend.

472
00:28:20,164 --> 00:28:21,339
-How you doing?
-Hello.

473
00:28:21,441 --> 00:28:23,035
Uncle Willie Earl.

474
00:28:25,154 --> 00:28:26,586
Rich and fine.

475
00:28:27,681 --> 00:28:29,145
Fine as a glass of wine.

476
00:28:29,251 --> 00:28:30,680
And my cousin, Malcolm.

477
00:28:31,010 --> 00:28:33,825
I invited the two of them to stay here.
